{"tid":1158331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紐約市長白思豪宣布參選總統","createTime":"2019-05-17T01:37:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T01:57:37.000Z","uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5bf6288022241c2206135f57af7f12a77be92f8b","tid":1158331,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T01:37:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2019/05/16/2139243_522f9552e6bf9f2e4b75a4d43eb78432.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2019%2F05%2F16%2F2139243_522f9552e6bf9f2e4b75a4d43eb78432.jpg&h=3958ee31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紐約市長白思豪(Bill de Blasio)宣布參加明年的總統大選。<br />\n<br />\n現年58歲、民主黨籍的白思豪發表短片，宣布參加黨內初選。不過，民調顯示，76%的紐約市民認為他不應該參選。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隨着白思豪加入戰團，令民主黨內參加初選的人數增至23人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2139243/紐約市長白思豪宣布參選總統\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2139243%2F%E7%B4%90%E7%B4%84%E5%B8%82%E9%95%B7%E7%99%BD%E6%80%9D%E8%B1%AA%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E5%8F%83%E9%81%B8%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEX2sgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=bded49f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2139243/紐約市長白思豪宣布參選總統</a>"},{"pid":"06a30cefe8eb34d1f749f48a9273a2fac906bc00","tid":1158331,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T01:39:00.000Z","msg":"好事"},{"pid":"05cffb8100be9eeb0383a2e497ff20874a7a3e3f","tid":1158331,"uid":34410,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T01:40:08.000Z","msg":"白人、男人、基督徒、異性戀既民主黨員點會贏到初選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45e7ece9bc1201ba3010f52f13071d0e8c921f20","tid":1158331,"uid":237562,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T01:40:51.000Z","msg":"好似從來冇紐約市長做到總統"},{"pid":"9a14602e765abc2c1afbf0e894259c1dc77bc03b","tid":1158331,"uid":108201,"like":2,"dislike":0